room_title: Escape room "Serial Killer" by Escape Canton in Canton
room_description: Your group has been kidnapped by a notorious serial killer known only as “Mike.” He takes you back to his secret lair, then leaves for a short while. Unbeknownst to Mike, a former victim escaped his lair and left clues behind to help future detainees. Can you find them all and escape before Mike returns to finish the job?
